{"tid":247373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（哲學撚入）其實人生係為乜？","createTime":"2017-05-17T17:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T21:05:24.000Z","uid":14671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b920672be78fac684682ef775b97cd48683b842f","tid":247373,"uid":14671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"去到廿到尾，經常問自己其實人生係為乜，<br />\n咁努力賺錢，為名為利係為乜？<br />\n到最後都係難逃一死，其實人生存既意義係咩？<br />\n有乜哲學撚或者宗教撚可以解答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我思考左好多日，只係覺得我暫時生存係為左親人，咁係未代表他朝有一日我無晒親人，我係未就無生存落去既必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：屋企環境尚可，有樓有老婆無小朋友"},{"pid":"a77ddfb869f0b309b988fa28b292a7382ac1953d","tid":247373,"uid":107774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"生存為左開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己開心就得"},{"pid":"663b8ba10cdc855fb355d8e8a6d7a26fee220e4e","tid":247373,"uid":80441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:24:55.000Z","msg":"冇好想做既事咩？"},{"pid":"01904dcb0cc3162632ea3e55437db0ad1df13996","tid":247373,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"繁衍"},{"pid":"03780553cb8b562b35a24664ada9a3bd604e4dd6","tid":247373,"uid":14671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生存為左開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己開心就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又唔係唔開心，但只係突然思考緊呢個問題"},{"pid":"cc1f2b98e9d16245f2f8f4be83b7844355d15c19","tid":247373,"uid":14671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇好想做既事咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有興趣，有想做既事<br />\n但係只係有呢個問題存雄係我個腦入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重申：我唔係想自殺之類，只係睇下有無人可以從哲學或宗教角度為我釋疑"},{"pid":"c7995e7916e652855f48c6d091d3382a0a357e15","tid":247373,"uid":14671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇好想做既事咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有興趣，有想做既事<br />\n但係只係有呢個問題存在係我個腦入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重申：我唔係想自殺之類，只係睇下有無人可以從哲學或宗教角度為我釋疑</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7178d778857bf67a04f43da43cece380e46bc667","tid":247373,"uid":6577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:29:28.000Z","msg":"你既然開心點解要諗咁多無謂野搞到自己唔開心 有樓有老婆已經好好"},{"pid":"24e550739d4a1c86f7b9ec1913b8e8de9c5a4326","tid":247373,"uid":99039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"如果咁易就俾你諗到人生嘅意義<br />\n咁你估你仲會唔會繼續做人？"},{"pid":"a70b51c81958020ae2e78fe1a01d0393800391b0","tid":247373,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:34:08.000Z","msg":"首先滿足自己生活需求 然後去幫有需要既人 或者成就自己既目標 最好自己既目標可以同時間幫到D人/推動社會進步"},{"pid":"4a6d3a46d02efab95d68abd096eb0bf3523584c5","tid":247373,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"人生係為咩 我諗個個唔同 <br />\n但係一樣既係大家都曾經懷疑過自我 為咩繼續生存<br />\n我覺得唔好比個意義兩個字去束縛 人生就係過好每一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n挂"},{"pid":"4bc2d9cfabfa39a6a7337096dceae8215069e0bb","tid":247373,"uid":62691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:36:07.000Z","msg":"人生存係為左死"},{"pid":"73460177935d0e79ff0c762b6675d817dc7f2387","tid":247373,"uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:39:06.000Z","msg":"追求"},{"pid":"c0b43191ab3cc5f208f1ca32a21385924f82870b","tid":247373,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"體驗各樣野？ 人生為乜呢個問題會聯想到死後會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8b97e587bf3e4aca4a9e3100801790669287c9","tid":247373,"uid":56729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T18:41:15.000Z","msg":"就係為左問你依條問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知呀<br />\n我自己都每日諗緊依樣野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9979ef4039792e95a93d587b52ee45439f0506","tid":247373,"uid":84691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T18:54:12.000Z","msg":"認識自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77792f45da96819843b26c081a84d859082ffa8e","tid":247373,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T18:58:23.000Z","msg":"咁要問下你自己點解你會問呢個問題"},{"pid":"783c3811d7494a5e34e6679d2c6acded9df87f90","tid":247373,"uid":90413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T18:58:24.000Z","msg":"我都唔知 冇特別興趣 冇咩開心野 成日都冇所事事<br />\n不過我覺得係尋找自我同快樂<br />\n好撚柒無聊呀屌你老豆"},{"pid":"345e126ff0ca3524726ed83dd99cb7d17cca9ff9","tid":247373,"uid":60231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T19:17:23.000Z","msg":"人生意義主觀黎講冇標準答案，只要你覺得一樣野係你人生意義，咁嗰樣野就係<br />\n<br />\n人生就只係機械式咁滿足自己唔同形式既外在內在欲望，<br />\n<br />\n我地人既存在=不斷地達成唔同目的，<br />\n<br />\n而人存在既目的=人既人生意義<br />\n<br />\n但存在本身既目的係現時未知既<br />\n因為我地唔知道 邊個創造人/人係咪被創造<br />\n<br />\n如果知道邊個創造人，咁佢創造人既目的=所有人既(客觀)人生意義<br />\n<br />\n如果人既存在係隨機發生，咁人生(客觀上)根本唔可能有意義<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"4ee83cab0ed7c7187ea36bbe4011315f2ee9a038","tid":247373,"uid":59669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T19:19:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生存為左開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己開心就得</blockquote><br />\n如果生存得唔開心<br />\n係唔係冇生存嘅必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b37ce4c56feeb810635095d1ce138f5f78eaa06","tid":247373,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T19:26:34.000Z","msg":"了解你自己同人性係咩<br />\n做你最有熱情既野<br />\n其他你自己選擇"},{"pid":"f18dd5367ba264b1ea0d4d4c274c36ed0936f96f","tid":247373,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T19:38:42.000Z","msg":"All the souls that would die just to feel alive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865d8bd9c9e942b73ae90f0415f13d720aa1d716","tid":247373,"uid":72226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T21:02:48.000Z","msg":"生命誕生。生命死亡  ,  生命應該係冇意義 .因為大家都會死,死左就乜都冇.如果生命唔會死,咁就應該有佢嘅意義喺度."},{"pid":"2672158a74f213309fe0f05f6c434b2a8fc11cc8","tid":247373,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T21:05:24.000Z","msg":"為夢想"}]}